    {
      "step": 3,
      "text": "이 조건들을 보니, 머릿속에 어떤 공식이 떠올라야 할까요?",
      "latex": "tan\\theta = \\frac{\\sin\\theta}{\\cos\\theta} \\\\ |\\cos\\theta| = \\frac{4}{5} \\Rightarrow \\cos\\theta = \\frac{4}{5} \\text{ or } -\\frac{4}{5}"
    },
    {
      "step": 4,
      "text": "이제 계산을 전개해 봅시다.",
      "latex": "\\text{From } |\\cos\\theta| = \\frac{4}{5}, \\text{ we have } \\cos\\theta = \\frac{4}{5}. \\\\ \\text{Then, } \\sin^2\\theta + \\cos^2\\theta = 1 \\\\ \\sin^2\\theta + \\left(\\frac{4}{5}\\right)^2 = 1 \\\\ \\sin^2\\theta + \\frac{16}{25} = 1 \\\\ \\sin^2\\theta = 1 - \\frac{16}{25} \\\\ \\sin^2\\theta = \\frac{9}{25} \\\\ \\sin\\theta = \\frac{3}{5} \\text{ or } -\\frac{3}{5} \\\\ \\tan\\theta = \\frac{\\sin\\theta}{\\cos\\theta} = \\frac{\\frac{3}{5}}{\\frac{4}{5}} = \\frac{3}{4} \\\\ -20\\sin\\theta\\tan\\theta = -20 \\cdot \\frac{3}{5} \\cdot \\frac{3}{4} \\\\ = -20 \\cdot \\frac{9}{20} = -9"
    }
